---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout showIntro={true}>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <canvas class="hero-bg-canvas" id="heroCanvas"></canvas>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-line"></div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">YENZ</h1>
      <p class="hero-slogan-zh">精雕完美，驚艷世界。</p>
      <p class="hero-slogan-en">So sophisticated, so perfect.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll">
      <span class="hero-scroll-text">SCROLL</span>
      <div class="hero-scroll-line"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Video Section - 米白色背景 -->
  <section class="video-section">
    <div class="video-container">
      <div class="video-title">
        <p class="video-label">BRAND FILM</p>
        <h2>島嶼心弦，雋永之詩</h2>
        <p class="video-subtitle">以台灣之美，詮釋品牌永恆價值</p>
      </div>
      <div class="video-wrapper">
        <iframe 
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ido7ko6CGnE?si=lgfPuuc_btdmZuNt" 
          title="艷世設計 YENZ｜品牌形象影片《島嶼心弦，雋永之詩》" 
          frameborder="0" 
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
          referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Brand Story Section -->
  <section class="section section-gradient">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-number">01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">EXPLORE YENZ</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">遇見艷世</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="brand-intro reveal">
      <p class="brand-intro-lead">
        設計，是為您的非凡品味，尋得最深層的共鳴。
      </p>
      <p class="brand-intro-text">
        在萬千選擇中，您與艷世的相遇，是源於對美學、對細節、對雋永價值的共同追求，一份精準而溫暖的品味對談就此展開。真正的設計，不僅是視覺的驚鴻一瞥，它更是一場情感的觸動，一份能經得起時間淬鍊，恆久流傳的經典。
      </p>
      <p class="brand-intro-text">
        2016年，創辦人瞿長緣，懷抱著讓世界為之驚艷的溫暖初心，在台北創立了艷世設計。她深信，每一個品牌都蘊含著獨特的生命力與故事，值得被以最精緻、最富內涵的方式演繹。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Eternal Knot Section - 深色背景 -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="eternal-knot-section">
      <div class="knot-visual reveal">
        <div class="knot-circles">
          <div class="knot-circle knot-circle-outer"></div>
          <div class="knot-circle knot-circle-middle"></div>
          <div class="knot-circle knot-circle-inner"></div>
          <span class="knot-symbol">Y</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="knot-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h2 class="knot-title">永恆之結</h2>
        <p class="knot-subtitle">The Eternal Knot</p>
        <p class="knot-desc">
          YENZ 的品牌印記，不僅是品牌首字母 Y 的優雅化身，它更是一個視覺化的哲學——一個生生不息的「永恆之結」。
        </p>
        
        <div class="knot-meanings">
          <div class="knot-meaning">
            <span class="meaning-icon">◇</span>
            <div>
              <h4>策略與美學的無限對話</h4>
              <p>卓越的設計源於策略與美學的緊密結合，兩者相互依存、彼此成就。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="knot-meaning">
            <span class="meaning-icon">◈</span>
            <div>
              <h4>根基與綻放的品牌生命力</h4>
              <p>繩結的底部穩固而緊密，象徵品牌奠定的堅實策略根基。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="knot-meaning">
            <span class="meaning-icon">◎</span>
            <div>
              <h4>信任與共創的永恆夥伴</h4>
              <p>與客戶之間建立在信任與共創之上的永恆夥伴關係。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Services Section - 米白色背景 -->
  <section class="section section-cream">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-number">02</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">SERVICES</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">全方位品牌解決方案</p>
    </div>
    
    <p class="services-intro reveal">
      艷世，讓您的品牌驚艷世界。我們為您的品牌量身打造卓越的視覺敘事與數位體驗。<br>
      從核心識別到虛擬場域，每一處皆是精雕細琢，旨在成就您的非凡。
    </p>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="service-icon">◇</span>
        <h3 class="service-title">BRAND IDENTITY</h3>
        <p class="service-title-zh">品牌識別策略</p>
        <p class="service-desc">讓品牌，成為一種信仰。深入探究品牌精髓，打造獨一無二的識別系統。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="service-icon">◈</span>
        <h3 class="service-title">VISUAL DESIGN</h3>
        <p class="service-title-zh">視覺傳達設計</p>
        <p class="service-desc">藝術與策略的視覺盛宴。將品牌訊息昇華為觸動心弦的視覺敘事。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <span class="service-icon">◎</span>
        <h3 class="service-title">DIGITAL EXPERIENCE</h3>
        <p class="service-title-zh">數位體驗</p>
        <p class="service-desc">優雅的互動藝術。為品牌打造連繫核心客戶的數位橋樑。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <span class="service-icon">❖</span>
        <h3 class="service-title">VIRTUAL WORLD</h3>
        <p class="service-title-zh">虛擬世界</p>
        <p class="service-desc">拓展維度的品牌敘事。VTuber 角色塑造與 LIVE2D 動態呈現。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section-cta reveal">
      <a href="/services" class="btn">EXPLORE SERVICES</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Promises Section - 米白色深 -->
  <section class="section section-cream-dark">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-number">03</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--forest-dark);">OUR PROMISES</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="color: var(--forest);">艷世設計三大承諾</p>
    </div>
    
    <p class="promise-intro reveal">
      信任是我們與您建立深厚關係的基石。為此，我們鄭重獻上三大核心承諾，<br>
      讓您的品牌之旅，從初始到未來，全程安心無虞，璀璨啟航。
    </p>
    
    <div class="promise-grid">
      <div class="promise-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="promise-number">01</div>
        <h3 class="promise-title">獨家匠造，彰顯唯一</h3>
        <p class="promise-desc">您的品牌值得擁有獨一無二的視覺符號。我們不追逐制式，亦不複製短暫流行，透過深度對談，傾聽您的品牌故事與願景。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="promise-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="promise-number">02</div>
        <h3 class="promise-title">智慧結晶，專屬歸屬</h3>
        <p class="promise-desc">您在艷世所孕育的每一件設計，其完整的著作財產權將毫無保留地歸您所有。我們堅持透明公開，讓您的權益一次到位。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="promise-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="promise-number">03</div>
        <h3 class="promise-title">專屬顧問，品牌遠航</h3>
        <p class="promise-desc">品牌發展是持續的旅程。無論未來您的品牌遇到任何疑問，艷世的專業團隊都將是您最堅實的後盾。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Founder Section - 使用真實照片 -->
  <section class="section section-gradient">
    <div class="founder-section reveal">
      <div class="founder-image">
        <img src="/images/founder.jpg" alt="瞿長緣 Chang-Yuan Qu" class="founder-photo" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="founder-content">
        <p class="founder-quote">
          我們始終以專業與熱忱，為客戶打造獨一無二的設計，共創品牌價值。未來，我們將持續精進，追求卓越。此志不渝，永矢弗諼。
        </p>
        <p class="founder-name">瞿長緣 Chang-Yuan Qu</p>
        <p class="founder-title">Founder & Creative Director</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Works Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-number">04</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">SELECTED WORKS</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">精選作品</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="works-grid">
      <div class="work-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="work-card-bg" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a4d3a 0%, #0d3d2e 100%);"></div>
        <div class="work-card-overlay">
          <h3 class="work-card-title">FOREDU 森知殿</h3>
          <p class="work-card-subtitle">台灣原生動物教育動畫</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="work-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="work-card-bg" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a5a4a 0%, #14352a 100%);"></div>
        <div class="work-card-overlay">
          <h3 class="work-card-title">長頸鹿藥師藥局</h3>
          <p class="work-card-subtitle">品牌識別設計</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="work-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="work-card-bg" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2820 0%, #061a12 100%);"></div>
        <div class="work-card-overlay">
          <h3 class="work-card-title">AINOMORI 靛之森</h3>
          <p class="work-card-subtitle">VTuber IP 設計</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section-cta reveal">
      <a href="/works" class="btn">VIEW ALL WORKS</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA Section - 更精緻版本 -->
  <section class="cta-section-enhanced">
    <div class="cta-deco-circles">
      <div class="cta-circle cta-circle-1"></div>
      <div class="cta-circle cta-circle-2"></div>
      <div class="cta-circle cta-circle-3"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cta-content reveal">
      <span class="cta-label">BEGIN YOUR STORY</span>
      <h2 class="cta-title-enhanced">
        讓我們為您編織<br>獨一無二的品牌故事
      </h2>
      <p class="cta-desc">
        每一個偉大的品牌，都始於一次對話。<br>
        從願景到現實，從概念到經典，艷世與您攜手，共創雋永。
      </p>
      <div class="cta-divider"></div>
      <p class="cta-sub">
        免費諮詢 · 專業建議 · 量身定制
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn cta-btn">START YOUR JOURNEY</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cta-particles" id="ctaParticles"></div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Video Section Enhanced */
  .video-section {
    padding: 6rem 4rem;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  
  .video-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .video-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .video-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .video-title h2 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--forest-dark);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .video-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--forest);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  
  .video-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(13, 61, 46, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  .video-wrapper iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
  
  /* Brand Intro */
  .brand-intro {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .brand-intro-lead {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .brand-intro-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  /* Eternal Knot */
  .eternal-knot-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .knot-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .knot-circles {
    position: relative;
    width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .knot-circle {
    position: absolute;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.3);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: knotRotate 30s linear infinite;
  }
  
  .knot-circle-outer { width: 250px; height: 250px; }
  .knot-circle-middle { width: 200px; height: 200px; animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 25s; }
  .knot-circle-inner { width: 150px; height: 150px; animation-duration: 20s; }
  
  @keyframes knotRotate {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }
  
  .knot-symbol {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    z-index: 10;
  }
  
  .knot-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .knot-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .knot-desc {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .knot-meanings {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .knot-meaning {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
